S.FORM: Leandro Barbosa unu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u misimaw zikuzay mimaliay mikilac zikuzay mimaliay. Leandro Barbosa i 2003 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 28, namapili' tu nu San Antonio Spurs putiput. 11 bulad 28 demiad, 1982 a mihca, Leandro Barbosa, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
